{"tid":2487453,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"行政長官全權委任資格審查委員會成員 坦言紀律部隊首長絕對適合擔任成員","createTime":"2021-04-13T14:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T14:22:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3024b3f8a1d2f457fa3cd91b7342449a95eb0640","tid":2487453,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥下午公佈《2021年完善選舉制度（綜合修訂）條例草案》，「完善」香港選舉制度。行政長官將全權委任候選人資格審查委員會主席及成員。被問及警務處處長及海關關長是否合適人選，林鄭指資審會負責判斷國安委的審查，坦言紀律部隊首長絕對適合擔任成員。<br />\n<br />\n官員任資審會主席 非官方委員須受審查、向中央備案<br />\n<br />\n在候選人資格審查委員會方面，委員會主席及成員將由行政長官委任，只有主要官員才可出任，成員包括2至3人。林鄭又指在吸納社會意見後，將加入若干位非官方的社會人士，但就沒有透露人選及數目。<br />\n<br />\n有記者追問資審會的組成，警務處處長及海關關長是否合適人選。林鄭指資審會負責判斷國安委的審查，認為紀律部隊首長絕對適合擔任資審委成員。她又指委員必須是愛國者，「要搵都唔係好難，我相信佢哋喺社會上都係舉足輕重，德高望重。」<br />\n<br />\n她之後又指委員有機會接觸到國安委的審查資料，強調「搵人要好小心」，「要搵人審查咗佢哋先」，並要向中央備案<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081998\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081998&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11LZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=c1595913\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081998&h=7eef2b69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081998</a>"},{"pid":"b5875ebbb9494ac546f7f306f46bf88fa930193e","tid":2487453,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6522f0d043d52fb5160a7a22a074a9015587b724","tid":2487453,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9a13aa9cd8d663aabbd52bca4b7a9d6ad08f8d","tid":2487453,"uid":265839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:17:47.000Z","msg":"軍政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e4ea736ea61bcd175793a2fc8a4c1a2b075c59","tid":2487453,"uid":54415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:18:08.000Z","msg":"犀利，為左police state連自己個位點check資格都俾佢哋"},{"pid":"5ee0d86bc5a20684823f77ee8731d1ae05b86e24","tid":2487453,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"叫警務署長做埋副特首呀笨"},{"pid":"1c2c15db13afab225c231d811e9670242476abc4","tid":2487453,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:21:47.000Z","msg":"中五起步毅進止步既學歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf1b75ccd89c9d13441e4ae2a399b2aa615b259","tid":2487453,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:22:17.000Z","msg":"無解放軍駐港司令<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}